title: Virat Kohli Wicket Video: Star India Batter's Off Stump Gets Knocked Over By Himanshu Sangwan During Delhi
text:
Virat Kohli's return to First-Class cricket was a disappointment during Delhi vs Railways Ranji Trophy 2024-25 match, where the batter got out for six. Kohli looking to play the expansive drive, ended up missing an inswinging delivery by Himanshu Sangwan, which came back from the deck and uprooted former India captain's off-stump. This was Kohli's first Ranji Trophy match in 13 years, having last played for Delhi back in 2013.
